# Development Tools

## Testing

### Unit Tests

- Unit tests for helpers, composables, or components in isolation.
- Co-locate with file under test: `[NameOfComponent].unit.spec.js`.
- Use `@vue/test-utils`.
- Quality over quantity.

## Node / JS / TypeScript

- Use npm for package management.

## Typing and Linting

- Prettier for formatting.
- Do not use type `any`.
